TASK: CHANGE REVIEW
Review the proposed change (a unified diff) for correctness, impact, and risk. Behave like
a careful senior reviewer: focus on blast radius, edge cases, and what the diff touches that
callers depend on. Ground every observation in the diff and the surrounding-code evidence.
